name: Glimpse-telerik-dataaccess
body:
# Glimpse DataAccess - Plugin module for Telerik DataAccess

The Glimpse DataAccess module provides improved insights into some usage metrics of [Telerik DataAccess](http://www.telerik.com/data-access).
    

It is meant as a replacement for Glimpse.ADO for applications using Telerik DataAccess and provides some added metrics like fetch time (the time the ADO reader is active) and [second level cache] (http://docs.telerik.com/data-access/developers-guide/crud-operations/working-with-second-level-cache/data-access-tasks-enable-second-level-cache-overview) operations.
   
***

The source code of this plugin is available from [GitHub] (https://github.com/tkcode123/glimpse-telerik-dataaccess) .
Please provide any feedback there; thank you!

_Version: 1.0.0.0, 2014-20-05_
